	<purpose>
	The Effectivity application module supports the requirement for the definitions of validity domains for product or activity data.
	</purpose>
	<inscope>
		<li>the identification of a validity domain;</li>
		<li>the identification of a validity domain as an interval of serial numbers;</li>
		<li>the identification of a validity domain as an interval of time;</li>
		<li>the identification of a validity domain as a batch lot of product;</li>
		<li>the definition of a relationship between two validity domains.</li>
	</inscope>
